\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Salavan is like, Mandrameen! Didn\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92t expect to see you! Where\u8217\'92s soreel? Whats the secret to your beer. I hear its date syrup, but every time I put it in, its got this sweet, cloying taste that coats the tongue and its terrible.}
